    "description": {
      "value": "<p>An eidolon's senses become incredibly acute, giving it blindsense out to a range of 30 feet.</p>\n<p>This ability allows the eidolon to pinpoint the location of creatures that it cannot see without having to make a Perception check, but such creatures still have total concealment from the eidolon.</p>\n<p>Visibility still affects the eidolon's movement and it is still denied its Dexterity bonus to Armor Class against attacks from creatures it cannot see.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>The summoner must be at least 9th level before selecting this evolution.</p>",
